        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2411",
        "content": "But she thought not of herself, and the animated smile she gave him, told how much she felt herself obliged for the preference of her father.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
